videos.description: Arizona State's Eno Benjamin takes the han off and leaps over the line of scrimmage for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: ASU's Benjamin leaps in for a 1-yard TD

videos.description: Off a direct snap, Colorado's Laviska Shenault Jr. punches in a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Colorado's Shenault runs in 1-yard TD

videos.description: Colorado's Nate Landman is ejected for targeting after hitting ASU's Eno Benjamin high.
videos.headline: Colorado Landman ejected for targeting

videos.description: Eno Benjamin runs in his second 1-yard touchdown to give ASU a 14-7 lead over No. 21 Colorado.
videos.headline: ASU's Benjamin scores his second TD

videos.description: Colorado's Laviska Shenault Jr.'s second touchdown of the game ties it up with Arizona State at 14.
videos.headline: Colorado's Shenault scores 3-yard pass TD

videos.description: Arizona State QB Manny Wilkins threads the needle in between two defenders to Frank Darby for a 40-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: ASU's Wilkins delivers perfect pass for a 40-yard TD

videos.description: Colorado's Laviska Shenault Jr. catches a Steven Montez pass for a 30-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Colorado's Shenault cashes in 3rd TD

videos.description: Colorado's Steven Montez finds K.D. Nixon for a 51-yard catch, which later sets up Laviska Shenault Jr. for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Nixon 51-yard catch sets up TD for Colorado
